Class HomeMenu

java.lang.Object
login.HomeMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
WebHeader
public class HomeMenu
extends java.lang.Object
implements WebHeader
This class is responsible for displaying the Main Menu Page after User logs in

This class implements WebHeader which contains all the Strings of the Header and Options to be printed
